### 15. 查询主失物并提取 lostMainId
GET {{baseUrl}}/lost-items?itemName={{lostMainName}}&location=图书馆

> {%
const items = response.body.data || [];
if (items.length > 0) {
  client.global.set("lostMainId", items[0].id);
}
%}

