### 21. 用户A修改主失物
PUT {{baseUrl}}/lost-items/{{lostMainId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userAToken}}

{
  "itemName": "{{lostMainName}}",
  "lostLocation": "图书馆四楼",
  "lostTime": "2026-04-16 10:15:00",
  "description": "修改后的失物描述：蓝色卡套，证件较多",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/lost-main-updated.jpg",
  "contactInfo": "微信:api_user_a_updated"
}

### 22. 用户B修改主拾物
PUT {{baseUrl}}/found-items/{{foundMainId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userBToken}}

{
  "itemName": "{{foundMainName}}",
  "foundLocation": "西区食堂二楼",
  "foundTime": "2026-04-16 12:15:00",
  "description": "修改后的拾物描述：一串钥匙，带红色挂绳和门禁卡",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/found-main-updated.jpg",
  "contactInfo": "电话:{{userBPhone}}"
}

### 23. 用户A删除待删除失物
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/lost-items/{{lostDeleteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userAToken}}

### 24. 用户B删除待删除拾物
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/found-items/{{foundDeleteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userBToken}}

### 25. 用户B对用户A的失物留言
POST {{baseUrl}}/comments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userBToken}}

{
  "itemType": 1,
  "itemId": {{lostMainId}},
  "content": "我好像在图书馆前台见过，建议去问一下。",
  "contactInfo": "微信:api_user_b"
}

### 26. 查询失物留言
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments?itemType=1&itemId={{lostMainId}}

### 27. 用户B给用户A发私信
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userBToken}}

{
  "receiverId": {{userAId}},
  "content": "你好，我可能见过你的校园卡，可以私聊确认。"
}

### 28. 用户A查看与用户B的私信会话
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/{{userBId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userAToken}}

### 29. 用户A查看通知列表并提取 notificationId
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{userAToken}}

> {%
const items = response.body.data || [];
if (items.length > 0) {
  client.global.set("notificationId", items[0].id);
}
%}

### 30. 用户A把第一条通知标记已读
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notifications/{{notificationId}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{userAToken}}

### 31. 用户B举报用户A的失物
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userBToken}}

{
  "itemType": 1,
  "itemId": {{lostMainId}},
  "reason": "测试举报流程"
}

### 32. 用户A发起失物置顶申请
POST {{baseUrl}}/top-requests
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userAToken}}

{
  "lostItemId": {{lostMainId}},
  "reason": "校园卡影响日常出入，希望优先展示",
  "topHours": 24
}

### 33. AI 生成失物描述
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/lost-items/{{lostMainId}}/generate-description
Authorization: Bearer {{userAToken}}

### 34. AI 重新生成失物描述
PUT {{baseUrl}}/ai/lost-items/{{lostMainId}}/regenerate-description
Authorization: Bearer {{userAToken}}

### 35. AI 生成拾物描述
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/found-items/{{foundMainId}}/generate-description
Authorization: Bearer {{userBToken}}

### 36. AI 重新生成拾物描述
PUT {{baseUrl}}/ai/found-items/{{foundMainId}}/regenerate-description
Authorization: Bearer {{userBToken}}

### 37. 用户A标记主失物已找回
PUT {{baseUrl}}/lost-items/{{lostMainId}}/resolve
Authorization: Bearer {{userAToken}}

### 38. 用户B标记主拾物已认领
PUT {{baseUrl}}/found-items/{{foundMainId}}/claim
Authorization: Bearer {{userBToken}}

### 39. 登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account": "{{adminAccount}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

> {%
if (response.body && response.body.code === 200 && response.body.data) {
  client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.data.token);
  client.global.set("adminId", response.body.data.userId);
} else {
  client.log("管理员登录失败，未写入 token。响应: " + JSON.stringify(response.body));
}
%}

### 40. 管理员查看用户列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 41. 管理员查看平台统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/stats?startTime=2026-04-01%2000:00:00&endTime=2026-04-30%2023:59:59
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 42. 管理员封禁用户B
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/{{userBId}}/ban
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 43. 管理员解封用户B
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/{{userBId}}/unban
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 44. 管理员删除测试失物
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/lost-items/{{lostAdminDeleteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 45. 管理员删除测试拾物
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/found-items/{{foundAdminDeleteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 46. 管理员审核通过举报
# 说明：当前项目没有“举报列表查询接口”，这里需要先把 @reportIdManual 改成真实举报 ID。
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/reports/{{reportIdManual}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "reviewRemark": "举报属实，已处理"
}

### 47. 管理员驳回举报
# 说明：如果你要测试驳回，请把 reportIdManual 换成另一条待审核举报记录。
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/reports/{{reportIdManual}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "reviewRemark": "举报不成立，驳回"
}

### 48. 管理员审核通过置顶申请
# 说明：当前项目没有“置顶申请列表查询接口”，这里需要先把 @topRequestIdManual 改成真实申请 ID。
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/top-requests/{{topRequestIdManual}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 49. 管理员驳回置顶申请
# 说明：如果你要测试驳回，请把 topRequestIdManual 换成另一条待审核置顶申请记录。
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/top-requests/{{topRequestIdManual}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 50. 管理员生成 AI 总结
GET {{baseUrl}}/ai/admin-summary?startTime=2026-04-01%2000:00:00&endTime=2026-04-30%2023:59:59
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
